ai:
Here is the translation of the song "Meaning":

```markdown
[Chorus]
We pick up trash on the streets, keeping the world clean,
Passing smiles to passersby, as if the sun shines upon the earth.
But these good deeds, like dust settling down,
Are but a fleeting moment in the universe's long river.
Are our efforts all in vain?

[Bridge]
We help the elderly cross the road, give up our seats to those in need,
Stop our cars before the zebra crossing, kind to the disabled.
But this warmth, like a meteor streaking across the night sky,
Will ultimately vanish, leaving no trace.
Is our care just a fleeting blossom?

[Verse 1]
We don't speak rudely, repair broken chairs,
Release small animals, buy fruits from the elderly.
But these actions, like grains of sand in an hourglass,
Will pass with time, everything will return to nothing.
Are our good deeds just a mirage?

[Verse 2]
We give directions to the lost, chat with lonely friends and family,
Share life experiences, tell stories to children.
But these stories, like bubbles on the sea,
Burst upon touch, leaving no memories.
Are our words just howling in the wind?

[Verse 3]
We do more for others, without seeking a return,
Create surprises for those around us, donate anonymously.
But these contributions, like leaves in the wind,
Will eventually fall to the ground, turning to dust.
Is our giving just an empty gesture?

[Outro]
We do all these good things, thinking we can leave something behind,
But ultimately, we find it's all in vain.
For humanity will eventually perish, nothing has meaning,
On the stage of the universe, we are but passersby.
Is our existence just a hollow joy?

[Final Verse]
But you, my friend, because I see you among them,
I feel what I do also has meaning.
Though fate is fickle, the world will eventually be silent,
But because of you, my world is filled with light.

